AWS management console
Amazon Elastic Compute Cloud (EC2) VM's in the cloud - instance ami
Amazon Machine Image (AMI)
Elastic IP addresses (EIPs)
AWS Identity and Access Management (IAM)
Elastic Load Balancing automatically distributes incoming application traffic across multiple Amazon EC2 instances. (ELB)
Amazon Simple Storage Service (Amazon S3), provides developers and IT teams with secure, durable, highly-scalable cloud storage (S3) buckets stores to at least 2 datacenters a little slow
Amazon Relational Database Service (Amazon RDS)
virtual private cloud - Provides an isolated virtual network for your virtual servers(VPC) allows VPN creation from local servers to servers in AWS
AWS Lambda - Runs your code on virtual servers from Amazon EC2 in response to events.
Amazon ECS Provides Docker containers on virtual servers from Amazon EC2
A security group acts as a virtual firewall for your instance to control inbound and outbound traffic.
